> test:1: Type error
>   (fn (a,b) { a })(5,if 5 { 5 } else { 5 })
>                         ^
>      found: int
>   expected: bool

# more tuple cases
fn (f) { (f({x:1,y:2}), f({x:1,z:2})) }
> fn (f) { (f({x: 1, y: 2}), f({x: 1, z: 2})) }
